import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import ProductsPage from '../views/ProductsPage.vue'

Vue.use(VueRouter)

const routes = [
  {
    path: '/products',
    name: 'Products',
    component: 'ProductsPage'
  }
]

const router = new VueRouter({
  mode: 'history',
  base: process.env.BASE_URL,
  routes
})

export default router
